              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/translation/lev-rubinstein-ordinary-life-through-lens-russian-conceptualism-daria-shchukina" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Rubinstein-A.jpg?itok=q3nINJUP" width="250" height="175" alt="Photograph of Lev Rubinstein in a collage effect" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/translation/lev-rubinstein-ordinary-life-through-lens-russian-conceptualism-daria-shchukina">Lev Rubinstein: Ordinary Life through the Lens of Russian Conceptualism</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/daria-shchukina" hreflang="en">Daria Shchukina</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/translation/niksen-veronica-esposito" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/EspositoNiksen-w.jpg?itok=719vLQm7" width="250" height="175" alt="A photograph of a person lying in the sun looking out a window" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/translation/niksen-veronica-esposito"><em>Niksen</em></a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/veronica-esposito" hreflang="en">Veronica Esposito</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/translation/different-coin-equal-sum-translating-kopilka-poetry-witness-and-antiwar-protest" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/KaneCoin-w.jpeg?itok=Hx5vPoMA" width="250" height="175" alt="A black and white photograph of a hand holding coins" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/translation/different-coin-equal-sum-translating-kopilka-poetry-witness-and-antiwar-protest">Different Coin, Equal Sum: Translating the <em>Kopilka</em> Poetry of…</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/yana-kane" hreflang="en">Yana Kane</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/translation/hygge-veronica-esposito" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/EspositoHygge-w.jpg?itok=hbd_3OYs" width="250" height="175" alt="A photograph of a person sitting in front of a fire reading" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/translation/hygge-veronica-esposito"><em>Hygge</em></a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/veronica-esposito" hreflang="en">Veronica Esposito</a>
</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/translation/wabi-sabi-and-art-imperfection-veronica-esposito" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Esposito-Anchor.jpg?itok=ViIn1Jbt" width="250" height="175" alt="A photograph of a pair of hands holding a mended bowl" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/translation/wabi-sabi-and-art-imperfection-veronica-esposito"><em>Wabi-sabi</em> and the Art of Imperfection</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/veronica-esposito" hreflang="en">Veronica Esposito</a>
